dc_creator_sm: United States. Central Intelligence Agency. Cartography Center
dc_description_s: This is a set of ancillary maps that make up a profile of the country of Iraq. They contain information such as population density, oil infrastructure,distribution of ethnoreligious groups and major tribes, kurdish areas of northern Iraq and are shown at a 1:2,000,000 scale. The map was created for use by Department of Defense by the United States Central Intelligence Agency Cartography Center
